[h1] The meta block

[p-]
An optional meta block at the very top of your file sets page-level
properties. Place it before any other content.
[-p]

[code-]
[meta-]
domain: yourname.podweb
author: Your Name
[-meta]
[-code]

[h2] domain

[p-]
Registers a short name for your page. Once a visitor loads your page
their browser remembers that name, so they can type "yourname.podweb"
in the address bar instead of the full podnet URL.
[-p]

[h2] author

[p] Optional display name. Not currently shown in the browser but reserved for future use.

